<h2>SURGERY SHOW PAGE</h1>

<%= @surgery.title %></br>
<%= @surgery.day_of_week %></br>
<%= @surgery.operating_room_number %></br></br>

Doctor's on this Surgery:</br>
Doctors: <%= @surgery.total_doctors %></br></br>

Enter doctor ID to add doctor to this surgery:
<%= form_tag surgeries_path(@surgery), method: :post do %>
  <%= label_tag :doctor_id, "Doctor ID: " %>
  <%= text_field_tag :doctor_id %>
  <%= submit_tag 'Submit'%>
<% end %>

<h2>Other surgeries happening this day of the week:</h2>
<%= Surgery.other_surgeries %></br>

Doctors on this Surgery:</br>
<%= @surgery.doctors.each do |doctor| %>
  <%= doctor.name %>
<% end %>